---
// Landing page component for TicketForge
import Footer from "./Footer.astro";
---

<main class="min-h-screen">
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav
    class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 border-b border-slate-700 bg-slate-900/50 backdrop-blur-md z-50"
  >
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-12">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
          ðŸ”§ <span
            class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >TicketForge</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="space-x-8 hidden md:flex">
          <a href="#features" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition"
            >Features</a
          >
          <a href="#problem" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition"
            >Why TicketForge</a
          >
          <a href="#cta" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition"
            >Get Started</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <button
          class="px-6 py-2 text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition font-medium"
        >
          Login
        </button>
        <button
          class="px-6 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-500/50 transition"
        >
          Try TicketForge
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Automate Ticket Assignment with <span
          class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >AI</span
        >
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        An AI-powered DevOps ticket assignment system that recommends optimal
        assignments based on engineer skills, past performances, and ticket
        requirements.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <button
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-500/50 transition"
        >
          Start Free Trial
        </button>
        <button
          class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-slate-400 text-slate-300 font-bold rounded-lg hover:border-white hover:text-white transition"
        >
          Learn More
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <section
    id="problem"
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 border-t border-slate-700"
  >
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Wasting Time on Triaging?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-4">
          Teams currently spend <span class="font-bold text-blue-400"
            >15-20 minutes per ticket</span
          > for triaging. This means:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-300">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-3 font-bold">â†’</span>
            <span>Understanding what the ticket is about</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-3 font-bold">â†’</span>
            <span>Assessing its priority level</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-3 font-bold">â†’</span>
            <span>Finding the right engineer to handle it</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mt-6">
          Instead of focusing on <span class="font-bold text-green-400"
            >resolving</span
          > the ticket, teams waste time on assignment decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-linear-to-br from-slate-700 to-slate-800 p-8 rounded-lg border border-slate-600"
      >
        <div class="text-center">
          <div
            class="text-6xl font-bold text-transparent bg-linear-to-r from-red-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text mb-4"
          >
            20 min
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-300">wasted per ticket on triaging</p>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-4">
            For a team handling 50 tickets/month, that's 16+ hours lost
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section
    id="features"
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 border-t border-slate-700"
  >
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-16">
      How TicketForge Works
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div
        class="bg-linear-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 p-8 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-500 transition"
      >
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ðŸ§ </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Intelligent Analysis</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          Our AI analyzes ticket content, priority levels, and requirements to
          understand the scope and complexity of each task.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div
        class="bg-linear-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 p-8 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-500 transition"
      >
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ðŸ“Š</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Engineer Matching</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          Evaluates engineer skills, expertise, past performance, and workload
          to match tickets with the best-suited team members.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div
        class="bg-linear-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 p-8 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-500 transition"
      >
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">âš¡</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
          Instant Recommendations
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          Get optimal assignment recommendations in seconds, reducing manual
          triaging overhead and speeding up ticket resolution.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 border-t border-slate-700">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Key Benefits</h3>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="text-2xl text-green-400">âœ“</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
                Reduce Triaging Time
              </h4>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                Cut ticket assignment time from 20 minutes to seconds
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="text-2xl text-green-400">âœ“</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
                Better Team Utilization
              </h4>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                Assign tickets to engineers with relevant skills and capacity
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="text-2xl text-green-400">âœ“</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
