              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="text-2xl text-green-400">âœ“</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
                Data-Driven Decisions
              </h4>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                AI learns from historical performance to improve recommendations
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-linear-to-br from-blue-900/20 to-cyan-900/20 border border-blue-700/30 rounded-lg p-8"
      >
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Potential Impact</h4>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-4 rounded">
            <div class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg">16+ hours/month</div>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
              saved on triaging for 50 tickets/month
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-4 rounded">
            <div class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg">20% faster</div>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
              average ticket resolution with better matching
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 p-4 rounded">
            <div class="text-cyan-400 font-bold text-lg">100% consistency</div>
